# Deep Dive Insights

## 1. Structural Profit Leak
Losses were not random — concentrated in:
- 3 sub-categories
- 10 states

## 2. Discount Abuse Pattern
High discounts (>30%) directly correlated with negative margins.

## 3. Customer Risk Blind Spot
Repeat customers were allowed to transact despite consistent losses.

## 4. Revenue Illusion
High-revenue categories masked underlying margin destruction.

## 5. Operational Gap
No real-time monitoring → delayed executive decisions
